reviewText: Very dissatisfied  I would love to have parts 2&3 unable to find ANYWHERE

Very good for study. Old film of dance styles so that you really get to see them both as solo and group work, sometimes partner work.
Helps you to really feel the transitions between  the Cakewalk and the Blues!.. in some of the jazz movements you must really study the transition into the later years but you can see the resemblance to African Dance.
